  <exercise>
    <title>Find the mean</title>
    <statement>
      <p>You are given the hypotheses shown below. We know that the sample standard deviation is 8 and the sample size is 20. For what sample mean would the p-value be equal to 0.05? Assume that all conditions necessary for inference are satisfied. $<m>H_0: \mu = 60 \quad \quad H_A: \mu \neq 60</m>$</p>
